01:10:19.895 --> 01:10:22.775
[MARATHI]

01:10:23.295 --> 01:10:35.381
Place your left hand towards Me. Bend
your head again and see. People aren't
doing it properly. Yes!

01:10:36.024 --> 01:10:43.724
Now see whether there is any cool or
warm air coming from your fontanel
bone area.

01:10:44.749 --> 01:10:55.139
[MARATHI]

01:10:55.139 --> 01:10:58.110
See for yourself and certify yourself.

01:10:59.575 --> 01:11:09.525
Yes, now put your right hand towards Me
and bend your neck, see on your
fontanel bone area

01:11:11.829 --> 01:11:19.489
whether a cool or warm breeze is coming
from your head? Bend your head. Yes!

01:11:19.489 --> 01:11:28.370
[MARATHI]

01:11:30.530 --> 01:11:38.270
Hmm! Now again, the left hand again.

01:11:40.224 --> 01:11:53.254
Bend your head and use your right
hand to examine your palate. Is
cool air coming or warm air?

01:11:53.254 --> 01:11:58.128
And now, warm air is coming because
you have not forgiven yourself

01:11:58.128 --> 01:12:04.388
and not forgiven others. That's
why warm air is coming.

