Raise both your hands and bend your
neck backwards to look at the sky

01:13:11.963 --> 01:13:19.143
and ask any one of the three questions
three times.

01:13:20.572 --> 01:13:24.942
You may call Me Mother or Shri Mataji.

01:13:25.122 --> 01:13:29.739
[MARATHI]

01:13:29.739 --> 01:13:40.586
Now the first question, "Shri Mataji,
is this Paramchaitanya?"

01:13:43.563 --> 01:13:50.103
[MARATHI]

01:13:52.570 --> 01:14:03.730
The second question, "Shri Mataji,
is this the Power of Love of God?"

01:14:05.690 --> 01:14:12.120
[MARATHI]

01:14:12.431 --> 01:14:21.411
The third question, third question,
“Is this the Rooh?”

01:14:25.393 --> 01:14:36.013
[MARATHI]

01:14:36.013 --> 01:14:42.566
"Mother, is this what is called the Rooh?"
Ask any of these questions, with your
heart, three times.

01:14:42.624 --> 01:14:50.434
And now bring your hands down. Put
them down. Now both hands towards Me.

01:14:55.748 --> 01:15:06.788
Both hands towards Me. Look at Me and
become thoughtless. Look at Me and
become thoughtless.

01:15:10.989 --> 01:15:17.889
There's no question of mesmerism in this,
because I've closed My eyes.

01:15:19.231 --> 01:15:24.321
People mesmerize with their eyes.
They do strange things.

01:15:24.875 --> 01:15:36.305
Yes, now look. Yes! Become thoughtless.

01:15:36.305 --> 01:15:43.214
Some people might be feeling a cool breeze
coming from under their hands. So they
should lift it up and bring it on top.

01:15:43.214 --> 01:15:50.016
Like this, like this, like this, like this.

01:15:50.375 --> 01:15:58.605
[MARATHI]

01:15:58.605 --> 01:16:02.347
[MARATHI]

01:16:10.894 --> 01:16:17.424
[MARATHI]

01:16:17.424 --> 01:16:23.755
[MARATHI]

01:16:33.054 --> 01:16:47.534
[MARATHI]

01:16:49.380 --> 01:16:54.050
[MARATHI]

01:16:54.050 --> 01:17:00.430
Experience must come
[MARATHI]

01:17:00.430 --> 01:17:09.366
Those, those - [MARATHI]

01:17:09.366 --> 01:17:16.769
Wow! Infinite blessings, infinite
blessings to all!

01:17:17.709 --> 01:17:25.899
Wow! Wow! Wow! Wow! How many people,
look how many people you are!

01:17:25.899 --> 01:17:32.631
If you settle down in Sahaja, you will
set the whole of Maharashtra right.

01:17:34.392 --> 01:17:42.342
Today you have to promise only this
to Mother, "We will settle down, Mother.
From seeds we will grow into trees."

01:17:42.407 --> 01:17:47.487
Just give Me this promise and I don't
want anything else from you.

01:17:47.487 --> 01:17:52.548
So live happily. A Mother wants to share
all Her Powers with Her children.

01:17:52.548 --> 01:18:02.560
Give everything, somehow, after convincing,
to everyone. Eternal blessings to all!

01:18:05.964 --> 01:18:13.564
Now please sit quietly for a while. I
have spoken about Gyandevji's 'Pasaydaan".

01:18:15.819 --> 01:18:20.709
So, someone has come and she will recite.
Its meaning is very beautiful.

01:18:20.827 --> 01:18:33.207
The meaning is that those who are the
speaking oceans, meaning the speaking
group(collective) –

01:18:33.207 --> 01:18:44.071
now all these have come - they walk,
and whoever

01:18:45.115 --> 01:18:58.505
came speaking - that whatever is,
(UNCLEAR) and all these forests,
the forests of 'Kalptaru' -

01:18:58.505 --> 01:19:03.295
All these people, the forests of 'Kalptaru',
have come - they go - it's all like this -

01:19:03.295 --> 01:19:06.699
But the first is, "Give us Pasaydan."
This is Pasaydan(Gift of Divine Grace).

01:19:06.769 --> 01:19:14.899
This is what they have asked for.
"I have seen this through your words,
now please give us your Gift of
Divine Grace(Pasaydaan)."

01:19:14.899 --> 01:19:20.966
Give this, this is the Payasadan.
Okay, now, sit quietly. Now one ...

